        "explanationThai": "'When did the Street Play Scheme first take place' ในโจทย์ถูกขยายความในเสียงว่า \"LY: So the second position might suit you better as far as the location goes; that's for a warehouse\" ซึ่งสอดคล้องกับตัวเลือก A (two years ago) จึงตอบ A",
        "questionText": "Street Play Scheme\nWhen did the Street Play Scheme first take place?\nA two years ago\nB three years ago\nC six years ago",
