        "explanationThai": "'It needs further investigation.' ในโจทย์ถูกขยายความในเสียงว่า \"last, you need a potter's wheel, a kiln, which is basically a very hot oven where you fire the pot\" ซึ่งสอดคล้องกับตัวเลือก B (It needs further investigation.) จึงเลือก B เป็นหนึ่งในสองคำตอบ",
        "questionText": "Which TWO opinions do both the students express about the evolutionary theory of loneliness?\nA It has little practical relevance.\nB It needs further investigation.\nC It is misleading.\nD It should be more widely accepted.\nE It is difficult to understand.",
        "layout": "choice"
