        "passageKeyword": "MAN There's another company called Larch Furniture.",
        "questionKeyword": "What led the archaeologists to believe there was an ancient village on t…",
        "thaiMeaning": "The lucky discovery of old records",
        "explanationThai": "'What led the archaeologists to believe there was an ancient village on t…' ในโจทย์ถูกขยายความในเสียงว่า \"MAN There's another company called Larch Furniture.\" ซึ่งสอดคล้องกับตัวเลือก A (The lucky discovery of old records) จึงตอบ A",
